We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or applicable law. The most current version will always be accessible via the link provided in the game's store listing on the Meta Horizon Store. We will update the "Last Updated" date at the top of this document when changes are made. Continued use of the game after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.


